source (untouched)\n   590‚Üí‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ CLAUDE.md                 # Host CLAUDE.md\n   591‚Üí‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ .git/\n   592‚Üí```\n   593‚Üí\n   594‚Üí## Daemon Configuration\n   595‚Üí\n   596‚Üí| Variable | Default | Description |\n   597‚Üí|----------|---------|-------------|\n   598‚Üí| `CLOCHE_LISTEN` | `unix:///tmp/cloche.sock` | Listen address (unix socket or TCP) |\n   599‚Üí| `CLOCHE_DB` | `cloche.db` | SQLite database path |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9be06376-5a43-40f9-8380-030cf073c859","uuid":"a696b067-6d34-4c7f-9541-c8fe72705679","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/docs/USAGE.md","content":"3. Validation output from `.cloche/<run-id>/output/*.log` (output from previous script steps)\n4. Result selection instructions listing the step's declared results\n\n## Project Directory Layout\n\n```\nmy-project/\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ .cloche/\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ develop.cloche        # Container workflow definition\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ host.cloche           # Host orchestration workflow (runs on host)\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Dockerfile            # Container image\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ config.toml           # Project configuration (orchestration, evolution)\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ prompts/\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ implement.md      # Prompt templates\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ fix.md\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ update-docs.md\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ scripts/\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ prepare-prompt.sh # Host-side prompt generation script\n‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ overrides/            # Files copied on top of /workspace/ in container\n‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ CLAUDE.md         # Container-specific CLAUDE.md (optional)\n‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ <run-id>/             # Runtime state (gitignored)\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ prompt.txt        # User prompt (from --prompt flag)\n‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ output/\n‚îÇ       ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ full.log      # Unified chronological log (status + script + LLM)\n‚îÇ       ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ test.log      # Per-step script output\n‚îÇ       ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ llm-impl.log  # Per-step LL